::steps{level="4"}

#### Add the Nuxt UI module in your `nuxt.config.ts`{lang="ts-type"}

```ts [nuxt.config.ts]
export default defineNuxtConfig({
  modules: ['@nuxt/ui']
})
```

#### Import Tailwind CSS and Nuxt UI in your CSS

```css [assets/css/main.css]
@import "tailwindcss";
@import "@nuxt/ui";
```

::
